NTG TOOL
========

This is a chrome extension created so that work would be made better.

Features:
---------
*  Automatic login (never again will I be bothered to login after a session timeout)
*  Automatic Session Refresh (see above comment)
*  Partial Redesign (Added constant Navigation with shortcuts and a lot of cleanup)
*  Custom JS Functions to make life easier

